ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: MERGE INTO databricks_mvp_workspace.informatica.bank_transactions AS t USING ( SELECT * FROM ( SELECT s.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER ( PARTITION BY Transaction_ID ORDER BY Last_Updated_Timestamp DESC ) AS rn FROM databricks_mvp_workspace.informatica.staging_transactions s ) x WHERE rn = 1 ) AS s ON t.Transaction_ID = s.Transaction_ID WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET t.Customer_ID = s.Customer_ID, t.Transaction_Date = s.Transaction_Date, t.Transaction_Type = s.Transaction_Type, t.Amount = s.Amount, t.Account_Balance = s.Account_Balance, t.Branch_Code = s.Branch_Code, t.Channel = s.Channel, t.Status = s.Status, t.Last_Updated_Timestamp = s.Last_Updated_Timestamp, t.Record_Operation = s.Record_Operation WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN INSERT * ;
